#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; Help System Handbook"
msgstr "Priručnik za KDE‑ov sistem pomoći"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help System"
msgstr "Sistem pomoći"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The help system is designed to make accessing the common &UNIX; help systems "
"(<application>man</application> and <application>info</application>) simple, "
"as well as the user documentation of applications including &plasma-"
"workspaces; from the &kde; community (&XML;)."
msgstr ""
"Sistem pomoći je projektovan da obezbedi jednostavan pristup kako "
"uobičajenim Unix sistemima pomoći (uputne i info stranice), tako i "
"korisničkoj dokumentaciji programa, uključujući plasma radni prostor KDE‑ove "
"zajednice (XML)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All applications (including &plasma-workspaces;) from the &kde; community "
"come fully documented, thanks to the efforts of the Documentation team. If "
"you are interested in helping with the documentation efforts, join the "
"<ulink url=\"https://mail.kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">mailing "
"list</ulink> and write to the team at <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</"
"email>. No experience is required, just enthusiasm and patience."
msgstr ""
"Svi programi (uključujući plasma radni prostor) KDE‑ove zajednice potpuno su "
"dokumentovani zahvaljujući naporima dokumentacionog tima. Ako ste "
"zainteresovani da pomognete u ovome, pridružite se <ulink url=\"https://mail."
"kde.org/mailman/listinfo/kde-doc-english\">poštanskoj listi</ulink> i pišite "
"timu na <email>kde-doc-english@kde.org</email>. Nije potrebno prethodno "
"iskustvo, samo polet i strpljenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
#| "language, review the information, including coordinators for each "
#| "language team, on the <ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org\">Localization web "
#| "site</ulink>."
msgid ""
"If you would like to help translating &kde; documentation to your native "
"language, review the information, including coordinators for each language "
"team, on the <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\">Localization web site</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da pomognete u prevođenju dokumentacije KDE‑a na svoj maternji "
"jezik, pregledajte informacije (posebno o koordinatorima jezičkih timova) na "
"<ulink url=\"http://l10n.kde.org\">veb sajtu lokalizacije</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Invoking Help"
msgstr "Pozivanje pomoći"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "&khelpcenter; can be called in several ways:"
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> možete pozvati na nekoliko načina:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu"
msgstr "preko menija <guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common will probably be from within an application. Choose "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Help</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem><replaceable>Application</replaceable> Handbook</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> to open that application's handbook."
msgstr ""
"Najuobičajenije je verovatno iz programa u kojem radite. Izaberite "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F1</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Pomoć</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Priručnik za "
"<replaceable>program</replaceable></guimenuitem></menuchoice> da otvorite "
"priručnik tog programa."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the Application Launcher"
msgstr "preko pokretača programa"

# rewrite-msgid: /Choose/Click/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the big <guiicon>K</guiicon> in your panel, and select "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem> from the <guimenuitem>Applications</"
"guimenuitem> tab or type <userinput>help</userinput> followed by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem>. This will open &khelpcenter; with the "
"default start page."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na veliko dugme K na panelu, pa izaberite <guimenuitem>Pomoć</"
"guimenuitem> pod jezičkom <guimenuitem>Programi</guimenuitem>, ili unesite "
"<userinput>pomoć</userinput> i izaberite <guimenuitem>Pomoć</guimenuitem>. "
"Ovim ćete otvoriti <application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> na "
"podrazumevanoj početnoj stranici."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "From the command line"
msgstr "preko komandne linije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; may be started using a &URL; to display a file. &URL;s have "
"been added for <command>info</command> and <command>man</command> pages "
"also. You can use them as follows:"
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> možete pokrenuti zadavanjem URL‑a "
"fajla koji treba prikazati. Postoje URL‑ovi i za uputne i info stranice. "
"Koristite ih ovako:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application help file"
msgstr "fajl pomoći programa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>help:/<replaceable>kwrite</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the &kwrite; help file, at the contents page."
msgstr ""
"Otvara fajl pomoći <application>K‑pisanja</application>, na stranici "
"sadržaja."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "A local &URL;"
msgstr "lokalni URL"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>file:/<replaceable>usr/local/src/qt/"
"html/index.html</replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Man page"
msgstr "uputna stranica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>man:/<replaceable>strcpy</"
"replaceable></option>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "An Info page"
msgstr "info stranica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>khelpcenter</command> <option>info:/<replaceable>gcc</replaceable></"
"option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking <command>khelpcenter</command> with no parameters opens the default "
"start page."
msgstr ""
"Izvršavanje <command>khelpcenter</command> bez argumenata otvara "
"podrazumevanu početnu stranicu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface"
msgstr "Sučelje <application>K‑centra-pomoći</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &khelpcenter; interface consists of two panes of information."
msgstr ""
"Sučelje <application>K‑centra-pomoći</application> sastoji se od dva okna sa "
"podacima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolbar and menus are explained further in <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Traka alatki i meniji pobliže su objašnjeni pod <xref linkend=\"menu-and-"
"toolbar-ref\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Documents contain their own navigation tools, enabling you to move either "
"sequentially through a document, using <guilabel>Next</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Previous</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> links, or "
"to move around in a less structured manner, using hyperlinks."
msgstr ""
"Dokumenti imaju sopstvene alatke za kretanje, tako da se možete ili kretati "
"redom kroz dokument, preko veza <guilabel>Sledeći</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Prethodno</guilabel> i <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel>, ili skakati "
"okolo koristeći hiperveze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Links can take you to other parts of the same document, or to a different "
"document, and you can use the <guiicon>Back</guiicon> (Left pointing arrow) "
"or <guiicon>Forward</guiicon> (Right pointing arrow) icons on the toolbar to "
"move through the documents you have viewed in this session."
msgstr ""
"Veze vas odvode u druge delove istog dokumenta, ili u druge dokumente. "
"Možete kliktati na ikonice strelice ulevo i strelice udesno na traci alatki "
"za kretanje unazad i unapred kroz dokument koje ste posetili u ovoj sesiji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The two panes display the contents of the help system, and the help files "
"themselves, on the left and right respectively."
msgstr ""
"Dva okna prikazuju sadržaj sistema pomoći (levo) i same fajlove pomoći "
"(desno)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Pane"
msgstr "Okno <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane in &khelpcenter; is displayed on the left hand side of the "
"window. As you might expect, you can move the splitter bar, to make sure you "
"can comfortably read the contents of either pane."
msgstr ""
"Okno sadržaja stoji na levo strani prozora <application>K‑centra-pomoći</"
"application>. Kao što biste očekivali, možete pomerati razdvajačku traku "
"tako da namestite udobnu širinu za čitanje bilo kojeg od dva okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents pane is further divided into three tabs, one containing a <link "
"linkend=\"contents-tab\">tree view</link> showing all the help information "
"&khelpcenter; is aware of, and the other contains the &kde; <link linkend="
"\"kde-glossary\">glossary</link> of terms. On the third tab you can "
"configure the <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Okno sadržaja je dalje podeljeno u tri jezička, od kojih jedan sadrži <link "
"linkend=\"contents-tab\">prikaz stabla</link> svih delova pomoći za koje "
"<application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> zna, drugi KDE‑ov <link linkend="
"\"kde-glossary\">pojmovnik</link>, a treći opcije pretrage koje možete da "
"podesite."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab contains the following default top "
"level entries in the tree view:"
msgstr ""
"Jezičak <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel> sadrži sledeće podrazumevane stavke "
"najvišeg nivoa u prikazu stabla:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fundamentals"
msgstr "Osnove"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Fundamentals introduce you to the many features of the &plasma-"
"workspaces; and &applications; and describe many common tasks you can "
"perform in all &applications;."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Osnove</emphasis> uvode mnoge mogućnosti plasma radnog prostora i "
"Programa KDE‑a i opisuju uobičajene zadatke koji se mogu izvršiti u njima."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma Manual"
msgstr "Uputstvo za Plasmu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &plasma; Manual is the documentation for the &plasma-workspaces;."
msgstr "Uputstvo za Plasmu čini dokumentaciju za plasma radni prostor."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Online Help"
msgstr "Pomoć na vezi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A page with links to online help and additional information provided by the "
"&kde; community."
msgstr ""
"Stranica sa vezama ka pomoći na vezi i dodatnim informacijama koje je "
"priredila zajednica KDE‑a."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Manuals"
msgstr "Uputstva za programe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Native &kde; application documentation. All &kde; applications have "
"documentation in &XML; format, which are converted to <acronym>HTML</"
"acronym> when you view them. This section lists all the &kde; applications "
"with a brief description and a link to the full application documentation."
msgstr ""
"Samosvojna KDE dokumentacija programâ̂. Svi programi iz Softverske "
"kompilacije KDE‑a imaju dokumentaciju u XML formatu, koja se pretvara u HTML "
"da biste je čitali. Ovaj odeljak nabraja sve KDE programe, uz kratak opis i "
"vezu do njegove pune dokumentacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The applications are displayed in a tree structure that echoes the default "
"structure of the <guimenu>K</guimenu> menu, making it easy to find the "
"application you are looking for."
msgstr ""
"Programi su prikazani u stablolikoj strukturi, koja odražava podrazumevanu "
"strukturu menija u pokretaču programa, čime vam olakšava pronalaženje "
"programa koji tražite."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Settings Modules</guilabel> entities"
msgstr "entiteti modula postavki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide a list of links to various modules in the &systemsettings; "
"application or to modules for &konqueror;, Filemanager or Browser."
msgstr ""
"Spisak veza ka različitim modulima Sistemskih postavki, ili modulima "
"<application>K‑osvajača</application> (kao menadžera fajlova ili pregledača)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "KInfoCenter Modules"
msgstr "Moduli K‑infocentra"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains a list of links to various KInfocenter modules documentation."
msgstr ""
"Spisak veza ka dokumentaciji različitih modula <application>K‑infocentra</"
"application>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "KIO Workers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Contains a list of links to various <acronym>KIO</acronym> modules "
"documentation."
msgstr "Spisak veza ka dokumentaciji različitih U/I zahvata."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "&UNIX; manual pages"
msgstr "Uputne stranice naredbi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&UNIX; man pages are the traditional on-line documentation format for &UNIX; "
"systems. Most programs on your system will have a man page. In addition, man "
"pages exist for programming functions and file formats."
msgstr ""
"Unix uputne stranice su tradicionalni format dokumentacije na vezi za Unix "
"sisteme. Većina programa na sistemu ima uputnu stranicu. Pored toga, uputne "
"stranice postoje i za programerske funkcije i formate fajlova."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollkeeper"
msgstr "Čuvar svitaka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional non-&kde; documentation installed on your system."
msgstr "Dodatna, ne-KDE dokumentacija instalirana na sistemu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browse Info Pages"
msgstr "Pregledanje info stranica"

# rewrite-msgid: /emacs/Emacs (the text editor)/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"TeXinfo documentation is used by many &GNU; applications, including "
"<command>gcc</command> (the C/C++ compiler), <command>emacs</command>, and "
"many others."
msgstr ""
"TeXinfo dokumentacija, koju koriste mnogi GNU‑ovi programi. Tu spadaju GCC "
"(kompilator C‑a i C++a), Emacs (uređivač teksta), i mnogi drugi."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Search Options</guilabel> tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Opcije pretrage</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching the help files is fairly intuitive, enter the word(s) you wish to "
"search for in the text box, choose your options (if any), and press "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton>. The results display in the viewer pane to the "
"right."
msgstr ""
"Traženje kroz fajlove pomoći prilično je intuitivno: unesite reči koje "
"želite da potražite u polje teksta, izaberite opcije (ako ih ima) i kliknite "
"na <guibutton>Traži</guibutton>. Rezultati će biti prikazani u polju "
"prikazivača desno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Search is not case sensitive, &ie; uppercase and lowercase characters are "
"considered the same. For example, if you search for <quote>Shortcut</quote>, "
"results that contain <quote>shortcut</quote> will be returned as well."
msgstr ""
"Pretraga ne razlikuje veličinu slova, tj. velika i mala slova smatraju se "
"istim. Na primer, ako potražite „prečica“ dobićete i rezultate koji sadrže "
"„Prečica“."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "The options available are:"
msgstr "Dostupne su sledeće opcije:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Method"
msgstr "Metod:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose how to search for multiple words. If you choose <guilabel>and</"
"guilabel>, results are returned only if all your search terms are included "
"in the page. <guilabel>or</guilabel> returns results if <emphasis>any</"
"emphasis> of the search terms are found."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite kako se traži po više reči. Ako izaberete <guilabel>i</guilabel>, "
"rezultat se dobija samo ako se sve unete reči nađu na datoj stranici. "
"<guilabel>ili</guilabel> pak daje rezultat ako se nađe bar jedna od zadatih "
"reči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If your searches are not returning the results you expect, check carefully "
"you haven't excluded the wrong search term with an erroneous setting."
msgstr ""
"Ako pretraga ne daje rezultate koje ste očekivali, pažljivo proverite da "
"niste slučajno isključili neku reč pogrešnom postavkom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid "Max. results"
msgstr "Maks. rezultata:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid "Determines the maximum number of results returned from your search."
msgstr "Zadaje najveći broj rezultata koji pretraga može da vrati."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scope selection"
msgstr "Izbor dosega:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to select the sections where the search will be done. The "
"available options quickly select the most common option, while "
"<guimenuitem>Custom</guimenuitem> allows one to select single sections."
msgstr ""
"Ovo služi za biranje odeljaka kroz koje će se tražiti. Dostupne opcije "
"omogućavaju brz izbor najčešćih odeljaka, dok pomoću <guimenuitem>posebno</"
"guimenuitem> možete zadati pojedinačne odeljke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <application>Man</application> and <application>Info</application> "
"sections"
msgstr "Odeljci uputnih i info stranica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man pages are the standard &UNIX; manual pages, and have been in use for "
"many years on many operating systems. They are extremely thorough, and are "
"the very best place to get information about most &UNIX; commands and "
"applications. When people say <quote>RTFM</quote>, the Manual they are "
"referring to is very often the man page."
msgstr ""
"Uputne stranice su standard na Unixima, i već dugo godina se koriste na "
"mnogim operativnim sistemima. Često su vrlo detaljne, i najbolji izvor "
"informacija za većinu Unix naredbi i programa. Kada ljudi kažu "
"<foreignphrase lang='en'>RTFM</foreignphrase>, uputstvo na koje misle često "
"je uputna stranica."

# rewrite-msgid: /application/command/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The man pages are not perfect. They tend to be in depth, but also extremely "
"technical, often written by developers, and for developers. In some cases "
"this makes them somewhat unfriendly, if not downright impossible for many "
"users to understand. They are, however, the best source of solid information "
"on most command line applications, and very often the only source."
msgstr ""
"Uputne stranice nisu savršene. Ne samo što su detaljne, već su često i "
"preterano tehničke, jer ih obično pišu programeri za programere. Ovo znači "
"da ponekad ne samo da nisu predusretljive, već su i potpuno nerazumljive "
"mnogim korisnicima. One su, međutim, najbolji izvor proverenih informacija o "
"većini naredbi komandne linije, a ponekad i jedini."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you've ever wondered what the number is when people write things like "
"man(1) it means which section of the manual the item is in. You will see "
"&khelpcenter; uses the numbers to divide the very many man pages into their "
"own sections, making it easier for you to find the information you're "
"looking for, if you're just browsing."
msgstr ""
"Možda ste se pitali šta označava broj kada ljudi napišu nešto poput "
"<literal>man(1)</literal>. To je broj odeljka uputnih stranica u kojem je "
"stavka opisana. Primetićete da <application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> "
"koristi ove brojeve da razdeli mnoštvo uputnih stranica po odeljcima, čime "
"vam olakšava da nađete informacije kad ih tražite prostim pregledanjem okolo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also available are the Info pages, intended to be a replacement for the man "
"pages. The maintainer of some applications no longer update the man pages, "
"so if there is both a man page and an info page available, the info page is "
"probably the most recent. Most applications have one or the other though. If "
"the application you are looking for help on is a &GNU; utility, you will "
"most likely find it has an info page, not a man page."
msgstr ""
"Postoje i tzv. info stranice, koje su zamišljene kao zamena za uputne "
"stranice. Održavaoci nekih programa više ne dopunjuju uputne stranice, tako "
"da ako je na raspolaganju i uputna i info stranica, obično info stranica "
"sadrži ažurnije podatke. Većina programa pak ima ili jednu ili drugu, retko "
"obe. Ako je program za koji tražite uputstvo neka GNU‑ova alatka, "
"najverovatnije će imati info stranicu umesto uputne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating inside the <application>Info</application> pages"
msgstr "Kretanje unutar info stranica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Info documents are arranged hierarchically with each page called a node. All "
"info documents have a <guilabel>Top</guilabel> node, &ie; the opening page. "
"You can return to the <guilabel>Top</guilabel> of an info document by "
"pressing <guilabel>Top</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Info dokumenti su uređeni hijerarhijski. Pojedine stranice nazivaju se "
"čvorovima, i svi dokumenti imaju najviši čvor, tj. početnu stranicu. Na "
"početak dokumenta možete se vratiti pritiskom na <guilabel>Vrh</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Prev</guibutton> &amp; <guibutton>Next</guibutton> are used to "
"move to the previous/next page at the current level of the hierarchy."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Prethodno</guibutton> i <guibutton>Sledeće</guibutton> koriste se "
"za prelazak ne prethodnu ili sledeću stranicu na trenutnom nivou hijerarhije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a menu item within a document moves you to a lower level in the "
"hierarchy. You may move up the hierarchy by pressing <guibutton>Up</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Klikom na stavku menija u okviru dokumenta prelazite na niži nivo u "
"hijerarhiji. Nagore u hijerarhiji vraćate se klikom na <guibutton>Gore</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Man is treated similarly to info, with the section index being the Top node "
"and each man page on the level below. Man entries are one page long."
msgstr ""
"Uputne su date slično kao info stranice, tako da je indeks odeljka najviši "
"čvor, a svaka uputna stranica nivo ispod. Jednoj uputnoj stranici odgovara "
"tačno jedna stranica pomoći."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kde; glossary"
msgstr "Pojmovnik KDE‑a"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The glossary provides a quick reference point, where you can look up the "
"definitions of words that may be unfamiliar to you. These range from &kde; "
"specific applications and technologies, through to general &UNIX; computing "
"terms."
msgstr ""
"Pojmovnik služi brzim upitima za definicije pojmova iza reči koje su vam "
"nepoznate. Kreću se od programa i tehnologija posebnih za KDE, do opštih "
"termina u Unix računarstvu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the left hand pane you will see a tree view, with two choices: "
"<guilabel>Alphabetically</guilabel> or <guilabel>By Topic</guilabel>. Both "
"contain the same entries, sorted differently, to allow you to quickly find "
"the item of interest."
msgstr ""
"U levom oknu možete videti prikaz stabla, u jednom od dva oblika: "
"<guilabel>Abecedno</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Po temi</guilabel>. Oba navode "
"iste stavke, ali drugačije poređane, kako biste brzo našli ono što vas "
"zanima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate down the tree views to the left, and items you select will be "
"displayed on the right."
msgstr ""
"Dok se krećete prikazom stabla levo, stavke koje budete birali prikazivaće "
"se desno."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus and toolbar"
msgstr "Meniji i trake alatki"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&khelpcenter; has a very minimal interface, allowing you to concentrate on "
"getting help rather than learning how to use the help browser."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑centar-pomoći</application> ima minimalističko sučelje, kako "
"biste mogli da se usredsredite na pomoć, a ne na upotrebu samog pregledača "
"pomoći."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "The icons available to you in the toolbar are as follows:"
msgstr "Traka alatki sadrži sledeće ikonice:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar Icons"
msgstr "Ikonice na traci alatki"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "Sadržaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490 index.docbook:719
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the main start page of &khelpcenter;."
msgstr "Ide na početnu stranicu <application>K‑centra-pomoći</application>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Nazad"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous page you viewed. Click the check mark right to the icon. "
"This displays a list of previously viewed pages. Selecting one will take you "
"directly back to that page."
msgstr ""
"Ide na prethodnu stranicu koju ste gledali. Kliknite na štiklu desno od "
"ikonice da dobijete spisak prethodno prikazanih stranica, odakle možete "
"izabrati stranicu da direktno odete na nju."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Napred"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go forward one page. This icon is only active if you have already used the "
"<guiicon>Back</guiicon> icon."
msgstr ""
"Prelazak na narednu stranicu. Ova ikonica je aktivna samo kada ste već "
"upotrebili <guiicon>Nazad</guiicon>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy text to the clipboard to be pasted in another application."
msgstr "Kopira tekst u klipbord, radi nalepljivanja u drugi program."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Nađi..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find a word or words within the currently visible page."
msgstr "Traži reč na trenutno vidljivoj stranici."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase Font Sizes"
msgstr "Povećaj font"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase the size of the text in the viewer pane."
msgstr "Uvećava tekst u oknu prikazivača."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease Font Sizes"
msgstr "Smanji font"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Decrease the size of the text in the viewer pane. This icon is only enabled "
"if you have previously enlarged the text."
msgstr ""
"Smanjuje tekst u oknu prikazivača. Ova ikonica je aktivna samo ako ste "
"prethodno uvećavali tekst."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "The menus contain the following entries:"
msgstr "Meniji sadrže sledeće stavke:"

