#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have previously moved back with the back icon or menu entry, you can "
"work your way forward again with this menu entry."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste išli unazad putem ikonice ili stavke u meniju, ovom stavkom možete "
